beamline.models.algorithms

    Package Description
    beamline.models.algorithms
    This package contains all classes of the framework necessary to have mining algorithms functioning.
  • Classes in beamline.models.algorithms used by beamline.models.algorithms 
    Class Description
    HookEventProcessing
    This interface defines the structure of the callback function that a StreamMiningAlgorithm can execute (cf., StreamMiningAlgorithm.setOnBeforeEvent(HookEventProcessing) and StreamMiningAlgorithm.setOnAfterEvent(HookEventProcessing)).
